<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/new-head', { title: 'Privacy Policy — Kidamame' , url: 'https://www.kidamame.com/privacy.html'
    }) %>

    <body>
        <%- include('../partials/new-nav', { alwaysScrolled: true, hideNavItems: true }) %>


            <!-- LEGAL CONTENT -->
            <section class="legal-content">
                <div class="legal-container reveal">
                    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <span class="last-updated">Last updated: March 9, 2026</span>

                    <p>At Kidamame, your privacy and the privacy of your children are extremely important to us. We
                        build our applications with the highest regard for security and safety.</p>

                    <h2>1. Our Apps Do Not Collect Child Data</h2>
                    <p>Our educational apps designed for children (such as <strong>Kidamame Discovery</strong>) are 100%
                        offline once downloaded. We <strong>do not</strong>:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Request, collect, or store any personally identifiable information (PII) from children.</li>
                        <li>Include third-party advertising or analytics networks that profile children.</li>
                        <li>Require you to create an account or sign in to play.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Any progress or state associated with the app is stored locally on your device and never
                        transmitted to our servers.</p>

                    <h2>2. Website Information Collection</h2>
                    <p>When you visit our website (<strong>kidamame.com</strong>), we may collect the following
                        information:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Newsletter Subscriptions:</strong> If an adult chooses to subscribe to our
                            newsletter, we collect their email address. This is processed securely via Substack and is
                            used solely to provide updates regarding Kidamame apps and announcements.</li>
                        <li><strong>Cookies & Analytics:</strong> We use minimal analytics to understand website
                            traffic. However, our website employs a cookie consent mechanism (Cookiebot) to respect your
                            tracking preferences. At this time, no profiling cookies are active on our site unless
                            explicitly requested by third-party embedded content.</li>
                        <li><strong>Support Inquiries:</strong> If you contact us via email, we will use your email
                            address and provided information only to respond to your request.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
                    <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal identification information to others. We may use
                        third-party service providers (like Substack for email newsletters) to help us operate our
                        business. We may share your information with these third parties for those limited purposes
                        provided that you have given us your permission.</p>

                    <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Opt-out of any email communications at any time (via an unsubscribe link at the bottom of
                            each email).</li>
                        <li>Request access to, correction, or deletion of any personal data you have provided to us
                            (e.g., your email address).</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>If you wish to act on these rights, please email us directly.</p>

                    <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time as our apps evolve or to reflect changes in
                        regulatory requirements. If we make significant changes, we will update the "Last updated" date
                        at the top of this policy and provide prominent notice if required by law.</p>

                    <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions about our Privacy Policy or data practices, please contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:info@kidamame.com">info@kidamame.com</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </section>


            <%- include('../partials/new-footer') %>
    </body>

</html>